&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 1rem;&quot;&gt;And We have certainly created for Hell many of the jinn and mankind. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 1rem;&quot;&gt;They have hearts with which they do not understand&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 1rem;&quot;&gt;, they have eyes with which they do not see, and they have ears with which they do not hear.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
