&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;So, what is the benefit of revealing it in the Arabic language, when 20% is still ambiguous for Arabic speakers? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Therefore, as soon as Muslims will claim that 20% of the Quran is ambiguous, then the Quran will automatically become a liar. &lt;/p&gt;
