&lt;p&gt;Al-Abbas said to the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ): We wish to sweep out Zamzam, but in it there are some of these Jinnan, meaning small snakes; so the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) ordered that they should be killed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grade: &lt;strong&gt;Sahih&lt;/strong&gt; (Albani)&lt;/p&gt;
